In 99% cases it's precisely estrogen, prolactin, serotonin, parathyroid, adrenalin, cortisol that drive all disease. Even when medicine admits their role, it still tries to word it as a "disbalance", "estrogen dominance" instead of just something direct like "Estrogen Syndrome"
